  <entry>
    <title>A new start</title>
    <link href="/2022/06/30/blog0/"/>
    <url>/2022/06/30/blog0/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="begin">Begin</h2><p>去年期末考试开始就想搭一个博客。高中搞OI的时候第一个老博客<a href="https://blog.csdn.net/segtree?type=blog">CSDN</a>由于太丑了用了很短一段时间就弃了，<a href="https://www.cnblogs.com/zzmmm">第二个</a>搭在博客园上用了竞赛组学长们的通用模板用到了现在，感觉这个风格还是很不错的，不过博客园这个平台感觉实用性还是不太好，一直想着换一个不同风格的blog。然而这个计划一直咕到了现在（上个学期虽然学分不多但事情都还挺多），目前在实验室学习跑训练等结果的时候就忙里偷闲基于github+hexo搭了这样一个blog，做起来还是挺快的，采用了<a href="https://hexo.fluid-dev.com/docs/guide/">Fluid</a>模板。</p><h3 id="style">Style</h3><p>之前搞OI弄的两个博客都是在记录写的题的思路和代码，第一个博客因为刚开始写博文文笔非常幼稚，第二个博客内容写的又非常意识流（现在看估计全不会了==）。现在打算还是认真对待这个博客，用来记录一些好的论文的阅读笔记和思路，然后为了卷那啥要记录一下ZJU-CS的专业课程笔记，最后还打算记录一下所思所想==。</p><h2 id="end">End</h2><p>我是菜鸡= =</p><h2 id="appendix">Appendix</h2><p>瞎几把写的一些东西，测试一下这个模板 <figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs python"><span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> frame <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">range</span>(frames):<br>           <span class="hljs-comment"># Forward action to the vehicle</span><br>           <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> action <span class="hljs-keyword">is</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">not</span> <span class="hljs-literal">None</span> \<br>                   <span class="hljs-keyword">and</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">not</span> self.config[<span class="hljs-string">&quot;manual_control&quot;</span>] \<br>                   <span class="hljs-keyword">and</span> self.time % <span class="hljs-built_in">int</span>(self.config[<span class="hljs-string">&quot;simulation_frequency&quot;</span>] // self.config[<span class="hljs-string">&quot;policy_frequency&quot;</span>]) == <span class="hljs-number">0</span>:<br>               self.action_type.act(action)<br><br>           <span class="hljs-comment"># record code</span><br>           rec_obs = self.observation_type.observe()<br>           self.road.act()<br>           self.road.step(self.config[<span class="hljs-string">&quot;total_time&quot;</span>]/self.config[<span class="hljs-string">&quot;simulation_frequency&quot;</span>])<br>           self.time += <span class="hljs-number">1</span><br>           <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> self.config[<span class="hljs-string">&quot;is_record&quot;</span>]:<br>               rec_reward = self._reward(action)<br>               <span class="hljs-comment"># rec_reward = self._reward(self.controlled_vehicles[0].action)</span><br>               rec_next_obs = self.observation_type.observe()<br>               rec_action = self.controlled_vehicles[<span class="hljs-number">0</span>].action<br>               rec_terminal = self._is_terminal()<br>               self.add_timestep(rec_obs,rec_next_obs,rec_action,rec_reward,rec_terminal,action)<br>           <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> frame &lt; frames - <span class="hljs-number">1</span>:  <span class="hljs-comment"># Last frame will be rendered through env.render() as usual</span><br>               self._automatic_rendering()<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>这是脚注<sup id="fnref:1" class="footnote-ref"><a href="#fn:1" rel="footnote"><span class="hint--top hint--rounded" aria-label="https://blog.csdn.net/segtree?type=blog">[1]</span></a></sup>，这也是脚注<sup id="fnref:2" class="footnote-ref"><a href="#fn:2" rel="footnote"><span class="hint--top hint--rounded" aria-label="https://www.cnblogs.com/zzmmm">[2]</span></a></sup></p><div>            <input type="checkbox" disabled checked="checked">todo          </div><div>            <input type="checkbox" disabled>= =          </div><img src="/2022/06/30/blog0/myblog\public\img\avatar.png" alt="p1"> <img src="/2022/06/30/blog0/myblog\public\img\avatar.png" alt="p2"> <img src="/2022/06/30/blog0/myblog\public\img\avatar.png" alt="p3"> <img src="/2022/06/30/blog0/myblog\public\img\myicon.png" alt="p4"> <img src="/2022/06/30/blog0/myblog\public\img\old_v1.jpg" alt="p5"> <img src="/2022/06/30/blog0/myblog\public\img\old_v2.png" alt="p6"> <img src="/2022/06/30/blog0/myblog\public\img\myicon.png" alt="p7"> <img src="/2022/06/30/blog0/myblog\public\img\avatar.png" alt="p8"> <img src="/2022/06/30/blog0/myblog\public\img\avatar.png" alt="p9"> ### Reference<section class="footnotes"><div class="footnote-list"><ol><li><span id="fn:1" class="footnote-text"><span>https://blog.csdn.net/segtree?type=blog<a href="#fnref:1" rev="footnote" class="footnote-backref">↩︎</a></span></span></li><li><span id="fn:2" class="footnote-text"><span>https://www.cnblogs.com/zzmmm<a href="#fnref:2" rev="footnote" class="footnote-backref">↩︎</a></span></span></li></ol></div></section>]]></content>
    
    
